Global Mosquito Repellent Watch Market Insights
Mosquito Repellent Watch Market size was valued at USD 0.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.20 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Mosquito Repellent Watch Market Overview
The global mosquito repellent watch market has experienced steady growth, with an estimated market value of approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2024. The market is expected to grow at a CAGR of around 8.3% from 2025 to 2030, driven by increasing awareness of vector-borne diseases and growing demand for portable, chemical-free mosquito repellent solutions. Consumers are increasingly shifting toward eco-friendly alternatives, and this has significantly contributed to the market's expansion. Technological advancements in product development, such as the use of ultrasonic frequencies and essential oils for repelling mosquitoes, are further fueling growth. The rise in outdoor recreational activities and travel is also driving demand for these wearable products, which are compact and easy to use for long durations, making them an attractive solution for people seeking mosquito protection without the use of sprays or lotions.

